            bindings = <
        &kp EXCL   &kp AT         &kp HASH          &kp DLLR        &kp PRCNT       &kp CARET          &kp AMPS    &kp ASTERISK          &kp SQT               &kp DQT
        &kp GRAVE  &kp TILDE      &kp MINUS         &kp UNDERSCORE  &kp QUESTION    &kp C_VOLUME_UP    &kp C_PREV  &kp C_PP              &kp C_NEXT            &kp FSLH
&trans  &trans     &kp LESS_THAN  &kp GREATER_THAN  &kp EQUAL       &trans          &kp C_VOLUME_DOWN  &kp C_MUTE  &kp C_BRIGHTNESS_DEC  &kp C_BRIGHTNESS_INC  &kp BSLH  &kp PIPE
